&lt;h1&gt;Staff Nurse Endoscopy&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;An opportunity has arisen for a part-time Band 5 Nurse to work in the Endoscopy Unit, 21.5 hours per week. The service operates between Hereford County Hospital and Ross-on-Wye Community Hospital and the post-holder will be required to work across both sites.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Endoscopy is an interesting and increasingly busy speciality and full training will be given.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Informal discussions are welcome – please contact either Fiona Goodarzi, Sally Plumb or Emma Baldwin on ext 1508’&lt;/p&gt;
